OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 29 APR
OL,4,CTEST CARDS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1983FThis would be the final day of
OL,7,Fregular daytime transmissions of Test
OL,8,FCard F on BBC One and BBC Two. From the
OL,9,Ffollowing Monday (2nd May 1983), Ceefax
OL,10,FIn-Vision would be used to fill gaps in
OL,11,Fthe daytime programme schedule. Test
OL,12,FCard F would be relegated to short
OL,13,Ftransmissions in the early morning
OL,14,F(5.52am - 6am weekdays on BBC One and
OL,15,Fpre-9am weekdays on BBC Two).
